description: This file defines the interface for the Cellular Manager Web Configuration API, including data structures, function prototypes, and necessary includes. It appears to be part of a cellular management system, providing mechanisms for version management and request processing related to cellular configuration via web interface.

methods.name: getBlobVersion
methods.description: Retrieves the version number of a specific subdocument.

methods.name: setBlobVersion
methods.description: Sets the version number for a specific subdocument.

methods.name: Process_Cellularmgr_WebConfigRequest
methods.description: Processes incoming web configuration requests related to cellular management.

methods.name: freeResources_CELL
methods.description: Frees resources allocated for cellular management.
